Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为戈薇再也不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不好好的跟戈薇道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人是怎么搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  八成是\N戈薇姑娘愿意妥协吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许犬夜叉和桔梗劈腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可置信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇居然能忍受这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犬夜叉太会钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在穷追猛打我想不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他从平常就没从容过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他也有点不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第49话  琥珀失去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是奈落的城的遗迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留着些许奈落的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连点痕迹都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的有座城才是怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是  现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也是把我们\N诱骗到假的城里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时看到的城是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落之城的确曾经在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  找到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家父的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候  我们这些驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被诱骗到奈落城里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  家父与同伴惨遭杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下手的人  是我的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子受奈落所操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸首就埋在庭院的一角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让令尊与大家的遗骨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弃置在这种不祥之地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把他们\N带到适当的地点好好供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说这里就是奈落的城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城中的那些人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚那\N受奈落所控制的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会也跟着城堡一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会被野狗挖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时就请各位安眠于此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在我们的村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的为各位造墓的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然村子里已经没有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还有我与琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人可以守着坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是琥珀他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙子  手艺真不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的看得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还让你帮忙砍柴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到屋里喝点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  有想起什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是自己从哪来之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最起码该知道自己的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在这个城附近的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概十天前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人见大人的城仿佛失踪般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天就发现你倒在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是经历什么很可怕的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会什么都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系  别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对对  在你想起来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎样都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  还有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量多吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我似乎曾在那里待过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公公  老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以千万不要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们这段时间的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从城里逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  城消失的晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有活下去的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你父亲跟同伴的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫…琥珀?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近了  就在森林那一带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目的也是四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  把埋在你体内的\N四魂之玉碎片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把碎片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那妖怪想夺走\N琥珀体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的性命全靠\N埋在体内的四魂碎片维系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片一旦被取出…他就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被奈落控制了心智…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在奈落的城里才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手腕受伤了  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我以前见过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从城里逃走前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落也不记得?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有活下去的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你父亲跟同伴的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  那就是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子一定是在演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看起来不像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  以前出现在\N我们面前的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛被抽走魂魄的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们两人独处不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为珊瑚说想和他独处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师的村落?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我们以前住在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我也能驱逐妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见习的程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下  待会还得工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你也准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经十一岁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也差不多该参与实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪真的会吐出火或毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们驱除的\N通常只是大蛇或大蜘蛛之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可怕的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些伪装成人形的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到四魂之玉的话就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  被奈落叫去的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是琥珀第一次上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你所知的  请全部告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛昔日的琥珀般…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖巧而有点胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点慢慢的回想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今后我们会一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不太好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是姐弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从奈落的手里逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扁他两三拳不就现出原形了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这么简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这是不是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昔日最疼爱的弟弟已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是陷阱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚会大受打击的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为奈落\N最喜欢玩弄人的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都不说的话  我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等不要这样子  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…关于琥珀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奈落的陷阱不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是想要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我除了相信还能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奈落的技俩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是我们及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片被抽出来话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟就会真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  这就是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好像因为\N自己在这里的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而害那个温柔的人遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是太疼弟弟才分不清道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆  你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好给我认清现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且本来就是犬夜叉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是一大群
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们难道是针对琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片的气息移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要保护琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们将琥珀藏起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想装蒜  他是奈落养的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀那家伙竟然趁乱逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片还在他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是来带他回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落也真是小题大作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过想要四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就带这么庞大的阵仗来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说目标是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  不过没了那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体就丢给他姐姐珊瑚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么追来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目标是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  不要再离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要对我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的亲弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  琥珀交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去阻止它们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲到那个洞里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在犬夜叉他们来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  珊瑚很强的  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你还没想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚是你姐姐的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚被迫和你分开后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间一直很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她平常很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时也会露出落寞的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以琥珀回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以和她在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话\N你就能想起她的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能想起那个人的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.67,0:22:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么可怕的东西\N我非想起来不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.28,0:23:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了她  杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破魔之矢用光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.54,0:25:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆被消除的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.31,0:25:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然受奈落的操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.41,0:25:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实行奈落命令杀害戈薇的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.75,0:25:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚知道这件事情之后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.02,0:25:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定杀了琥珀然后再自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现是陷阱而拼命的\N消灭毒虫与妖怪的弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉快一点
